Effective Date: [27-12-2024]

Links Terminator is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your data.

1. Data We Collect
We collect server id, role id (safe-role), channel id (logs-channel), words (banned-word) as these data are important for the bot to work.

2. How We Use Your Data
To provide moderation services.
To analyze and improve bot performance.
To prevent spam or harmful links in your server.

3. Data Sharing
We do not sell or share your data with third parties.
Data may be shared if required by law or to protect the security of our services.

4. Data Storage and Retention
Data is stored securely and is retained only for as long as necessary to provide our services.
Links data is typically deleted shortly after processing.

5. Your Rights
You can request the deletion of your data by contacting us.
You have the right to know what data we collect and how it is used.

6. Security
We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to safeguard your data against unauthorized access or disclosure.

7. Changes to Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Continued use of the bot indicates acceptance of the revised policy.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or the Terms of Service, contact us at our support discord server 'https://discord.gg/AdGr4YdNKA'.
